This template is intended for construction of specific info-box templates, it usually is not included in articles by itself. It generates a right-aligned, floating box, which provides a centered head-piece for images and left-aligned content-part for structured information about the subject it refers to. Info-box templates are created as sub-pages of this core template.

==Usage==
 <nowiki>{{infobox</nowiki>
 |heading=''images, description''
 |content=''structured data''<nowiki>}}</nowiki>

